name: Chic Hen's Harvest
description:
SAVE THE EGGS FROM THE HARVEST!!

In Chic hen’s harvest you are an over-trained rooster who must defend those hens and eggs.

Fertilize as much as possible to survive and protect them from the clumsy farmer and the rascal fox! The power of chicken’s team is in your hand, be aware ! See you soon, have fun and play hard. 

NO HOME LET
